<section id="PillarsSection" class="trust-pillars section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>{{ section.settings.title | default: 'Built for Long Hours at the Desk' }}</h2>
      <p>{{ section.settings.subtitle | default: "Whether you're working, studying, coding, or gaming, PostureTru helps you stay aware of your posture throughout the day." }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-4">

  <div class="pillar-card">
    <div class="pillar-icon">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Gentle Vibration. Real Awareness.</h3>
    <p>The moment you begin to slouch, PostureTru delivers a gentle vibration reminder. No apps. No distractions. Just real time posture awareness.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar-card">
    <div class="pillar-icon">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Build Better Habits</h3>
    <p>Better posture starts with awareness. PostureTru provides immediate feedback when your posture begins to slip, helping you stay mindful throughout the day.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar-card">
    <div class="pillar-icon">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Comfortable for Daily Wear</h3>
    <p>Lightweight and skin friendly, PostureTru sits comfortably against your upper back and can be worn discreetly under most clothing.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar-card">
    <div class="pillar-icon">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Try It Risk-Free</h3>
    <p>Backed by our 30 Day Satisfaction Guarantee. If PostureTru isn't the right fit for you, contact us and we'll work to make it right.</p>
  </div>

</div>
  </div>
</section>

